name: Surfside Girls
overview: Quick wits lead to daring discoveries for beachside besties Sam and Jade as they sleuth out supernatural mysteries in their sleepy hometown of Surfside. Based on the best-selling young adult graphic novels.

episodes.name: ...And the Secret of Danger Point
episodes.overview: As summer kicks off, Sam and Jade's bond is tested, but a budding mystery brings them together for a twisting-and-turning mission.

episodes.name: ...And the Untold Story of the Obsidian Flyer
episodes.overview: The Surfside girls learn what’s at stake if Danger Point collapses. In response, Sam goes hunting for ghosts and Jade conducts field research.

episodes.name: ...And the Lady of Surfside
episodes.overview: Sam, Jade, and Remi receive a new tip, but Sam struggles to balance the investigation and family time. Jade learns about the Lady of Surfside.

episodes.name: ...And the Promise of Peligro
episodes.overview: Grappling with guilt, Sam vows to make things right with her mom. Jade and Remi continue the search and uncover more about the secret cavern.

episodes.name: ..And the Weathered Storm
episodes.overview: Sam and Jade search for missing evidence and realize Remi and Captain Devar may be able to help if they can recall forgotten memories.

episodes.name: ...And the Day of the Flying Saucer
episodes.overview: The girls pivot from the supernatural to the scientific and make a surprising discovery, with help from Jade’s camp friends.

episodes.name: ...And Jade’s Journey
episodes.overview: A major break in the case leads to a friendship fallout. In the aftermath, Jade faces a swirl of emotions and gets heartfelt advice.

episodes.name: ...And Sam’s Story
episodes.overview: Sam makes a plan to prove she wasn’t lying. Remi urges Jade to make amends. Petey strikes a deal with Old Man Olsen.

episodes.name: ...And the Cursed Treasure
episodes.overview: As Surfside preps for the summer festival, Sam, Jade, and Remi work to track down a secret lair—and discover more than they could have imagined.

episodes.name: ...And the Showdown at Danger Point
episodes.overview: The summer festival arrives and the trusty trio orchestrates a last-minute change of plans to save Danger Point. But will it be enough?
